<s> Ooops, confusing terminology.  </s>
<s> SMTP involves sending a series of commands and getting a series of responses, with many commands per mail message.  </s>
<s> HTTP sends one "command" in the form of a message, and gets one response.  </s>
<s> So, while the concept is similar (and easily translatable for an HTTP - SMTP gateway), they are not "almost identical".  </s>
